commands.command.withdraw.description:
Redirects your funds from the bank back to your account

Please note that if you lose your funds, it is not possible to return them
commands.command.withdraw.brief: Transfers the amount back to the account
commands.command.withdraw.examples.0.des: Transfers 100 coins from the bank back to your account
commands.command.withdraw.examples.1.des: Transfers all coins from the bank back to your account
